data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: This picture describes a man standing beside a drying rack where many hats are hung. It seems like the drying rack is outside of the house which might be in an Asian country. The man looks Asian. He wears a white T-shirt and stares somewhere. I think he must feel like nothing to do. Moreover, the hats on the drying rack are colorful. There are white, green, blue, and red hats. Maybe this man runs a business for washing hats or selling hats.
